            <title>[CASSANDRA-13928] Remove initialDirectories from CFS</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-13928</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The initialDirectories added in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-8671&quot; title=&quot;Give compaction strategy more control over where sstables are created, including for flushing and streaming.&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-8671&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-8671&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; is quite confusing and I don&apos;t think it is needed anymore, it should be removed&lt;/p&gt;</description>
